Package sqltoregex.settings

Class SettingsForm

java.lang.Object
sqltoregex.settings.SettingsForm
@AssertMethodAsTrue(value="validateSQL", message="{settingsform.sqlInput.invalidSql}", field="sql") public class SettingsForm extends Object
SettingsForm is the connection between front- and backend. In this class is the sent form data's stored.
